comments: Kuzma (WAS) makes contact with Burks' (NYK) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Porzingis (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Randle (NYK) and absorbs the contact to his front.
Caldwell-Pope (WAS) makes marginal contact to the body of Barrett (NYK) during the drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Porzingis (WAS) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Porzingis (WAS) makes marginal contact to Barrett's (NYK) side during the screen and does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Barrett (NYK) legally contests Caldwell-Pope's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
